  "title": "Shot in the Dark",
  "description": "Shot in the Dark is BACK! This hit Fringe show is returning for a fourth year, and the stakes will be even higher. Try and catch which of our improvisers is under the influence as they all scramble to put on an improvised long form show like no other, and in more ways than one you’ll call the shots!",
  "credits": "<strong>Cast</strong>: Grace Fitzgerald, Madi May, Alex Sahli, Teio Suyal<br/>",
  "website": "https://www.instagram.com/scatterbrainimprov",
  "plain_language": "Shot in the Dark is an improvised show. One improviser has consumed alcohol, and the audience must figure out who it is by the time the show ends. The show is based on an audience suggestion, and is created live. This means it will be different every time! At the end, the audience guesses who was drunk.",
